document_data.History:
{{Quote|The goblins understand my appetites. They sate my hunger for gold and the rest sate my hunger for meat.}}

As of the {{YearlinkName|1492}}, Lump and his subordinates worked for the [[cult of the Absolute]], keeping post at the ruined town of [[Moonhaven]] on the [[Risen Road]]. In exchange for [[gp|gold]] and their choice of goblins to eat, the trio were responsible to ensuring that anyone that passed through town was marked with the brand of [[the Absolute]], lest they venture too near the cult's outpost at the [[Shattered Sanctum]].

Lump had no loyalty to the Absolute beyond his love of the gold and food they offered.
